Ekhuluma nesinye seziteshi zethelevishini, okhulumela abezimo eziphuthumayo KwaZulu-Natal, uMnuz Robert Mckenzie, uthe ingozi yenzeke eSipingo Beach. Ngaphandle kwabafile kulimale omunye umsebenzi kanzima waphuthunyiswa esibhedlela. “Udonga oludilikile beluseduze kwalapho besebenzela khona. Umsebenzi olimale kanzima uphuthunyiswe esibhedlela esiseduze. Okunye ngeke ngakuqinisekisa,” kusho uMckenzie. Okhulumela amaphoyisa aKwaZulu-Natal, uCaptain Nqobile Gwala, ukuqinisekisile ukuthi kufe abantu abathathu kwalimala oyedwa.